paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, west
description: The shouts of the roaring crowd from within the viewing stands to the south competes with the noise of the ringing anvils to the north.  Over all of the din, merchants call out sales to passersby on the road whose uttered curses in return bemoan ankle-deep mud and horse dung.  On either side of the way, freshly cut tree stumps are splashed with royal blue paint, some bearing detailed golden serpents.
title: [Rumor Woods, Hammer Way]
